      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t如果我菌封锁台湾，将会有很多大陆人死于饥荒。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-09-26",
      "agree_count": 4,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "692209",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "隔岸觀火",
        "uid": "102219"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t台灣人可以吃白菜拌飯撐一年，中國人可能真的要吃草一年了。\t\t</div>",
